::Striker::

Striker's eyes widen as he sees the fireball coming for him. He tries to 
dodge, but it hits him in the chest, sending him flying over a few trees and 
landing into another one.

The Maximal groans, falling through the branches, going into stasis lock as 
he hits the ground.
